1. *Takva* situacija se ne bi smela dogoditi. (Such a situation should not happen.)
2. Ona je tako iznenadila da je nije bilo *takve* reakcije. (She was so surprised that there was no such reaction.)
3. *Takvim* ljudima nema mesta u našem društvu. (There is no place for such people in our society.)
4. Ne znam zašto ga ona tako ceni, njegovo ponašanje nije *takvo*. (I don't know why she values him so much, his behaviour is not like that.)
5. Ne mogu da poverujem da je ona uradila *takvu* stvar. (I can't believe she did such a thing.)